stimulusHtml: What is printed as a result of executing this code segment?

features.html:
Consider the following code segment. 

 

String str = "lookout";
String target = "o";
int j = str.indexOf(target);
while (j >= 0)
{ 
   str = str.substring(j);
   System.out.print(str + " ");
  
   str = str.substring(1);
   j = str.indexOf(target);
}
